data.description: Looking for a home with classic character and charm without sacrificing space? This could be the one! Centrally located, kitchen appliance package, first floor laundry, primary bedroom on main level, spacious rooms throughout, gorgeous dining room built-in cabinetry, and so much more.  Seller improvements include eight new windows, new front door, water heater, central air unit, roof, furnace, water softener, flooring and carpeting just to name a few. Home exterior is Permastone and Vinyl. See what this home has to offer by scheduling a showing.
